\family typewriter 
/opt
\family default 
 or 
\family typewriter 
/usr/local
\family default 
 and issue the following command: 
\layout Quote


\family typewriter 
gzip -dc < thedistributionfile | tar xvof -
\layout Standard

Where 
\family typewriter 
thedistributionfile
\family default 
